    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It's not about free will or creativity, it's about safety and certification. The board thinks the high-level planning you do can be too unpredictable in complex traffic. Turning off the autonomous planning makes you much more predictable and easier to verify for the regulators. It's just a technical downgrade to ensure compliance.",
